## Additional Services Required

### Infrastructure Services (Not Yet Configured)
| Service | Purpose | When Needed |
|---|---|---|
| **AWS S3** (or Cloudflare R2) | Certificate PDF storage (v2), return evidence upload (photos/audio) | When moving from base64 inline â†’ real S3 URL for certs |
| **Celery + Redis** | Background job queue for async tasks (PDF gen, Agent scans, long-running analytics) | When synchronous Agent 3/6 scans start timing out |
| **Tesseract OCR binary** | `pytesseract` wrapper for invoice OCR parsing | `winget install UB-Mannheim.TesseractOCR` â€” before `parse-invoice` endpoint |
| **FAISS** (faiss-cpu) | Vector store for scheme PDF RAG pipeline | Before Agent 3 auto-ingestion from PDFs |
| **Embedding model** (e.g. all-MiniLM-L6-v2 via SentenceTransformers) | Scheme rule vectorisation for RAG | Alongside FAISS setup |
| **Leaflet geocoding** (optional: Nominatim / Google Maps API) | Converting outlet pincodes to GPS lat/lon for real Leaflet heatmap | Already added gps_lat/gps_lon columns to outlets table |
| **SendGrid / AWS SES** | Email notifications for certificate issue, return approvals | When email alerts are added |
| **Twilio / WhatsApp API** | WhatsApp-based return filing confirmation (v2) | Agent 4 action notification expansion |

